    <stitle>VT 275 Engine Service Manual - Fuel System - Assembly and Installation - HFCM</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc id="m7.5" graphiccount="0">
        <title>HFCM</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">CF - Install HFCM to chassis rail. Thread three mounting nuts (M8) onto mounting bolts (M8 x
                40) and tighten to the
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_278.xml" xrefid="E30013B" appearance="hottext">Special Torque</hotlnk>.
            </para>
            <para>Stripped chassis - Install HFCM to transmission housing mounting bracket. Thread three mounting nuts
                (M8) onto mounting bolts (M8 x 40) and tighten to the
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_278.xml" xrefid="E30013B" appearance="hottext">Special Torque</hotlnk>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install new retaining clips onto fuel hoses.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install fuel hoses onto HFCM cover plate.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect the water-in-fuel, fuel heater, and fuel pump electrical connectors.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Close water drain knob assembly.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
